➜最新出炉！厦门将新增两个口袋公园！这条路的绿化“月考”排第一～
http://www.sohu.com/a/427891571_100293506	13894
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">社区里拥有后花园</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">迈出家门就能逛</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">是不是觉得特别酷？</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img height="74" width="74" src="http://p3.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201028/ac7eaf0a507a4238921ab86c34ec82f6.gif" /></p>
<p><span>好消息来啦~</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>今年厦门将</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>新增</span></strong></span><strong><span>两座 <span>口袋公园</span>！ </span></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px;">都在哪儿呢？</span></p>
<p><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201028/be70b6f93e65418aa671da81d815b6b3.png" /></p>
<p><span><strong>振兴园和白鹭园</strong><strong></strong></span></p>
<p><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201028/a352563bedf9448c8813d3e7c379aa2c.png" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
